name: Nick Samoray
body:
### Introduction
Current Computer Science Major with a passion for and experience with mobile development, with a focus on Android and Hybrid mobile apps. Have created several applications both individually and with teams, as well as acted as a consultant to many student entrepreneurial projects involving mobile apps at Trinity University.

On my github you'll primarily find examples of my work with Unity.

### Support or Contact
Email: nsamoray@trinity.edu
